                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740413-96-off483 t17740413-96-crimeloc487"></join>, but I cannot swear to the man; I saw him bring a basket with rubbish seemingly down the ladder from the top of the hospital; I laid hold of him by the collar; I found forty pound of lead in the basket; I gave the porter of the hospital charge of him.</p>
               <p>
            
